{"tid":1628110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[叫春][不推文] 點解妳係港豬","createTime":"2019-10-06T00:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T00:13:17.000Z","uid":300918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af7f4977746e38d6e05e5774668d523d0b974607","tid":1628110,"uid":300918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:13:17.000Z","msg":"<em>回覆記得㩒不推文</em><br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚鍾意妳啊<br />\n但點解妳係港豬啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知唔知每次有遊行既日子<br />\n我提妳出門口返工小心啲時<br />\n我好想妳唔係剩係答我<br />\n<br />\n&quot;好啊, 你都係&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我想妳同我講不如一齊出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解妳連遊行都唔肯去<br />\n和你非都唔肯做<br />\n又話自己見到人地好慘會心痛<br />\n但又唔肯企出黎<br />\n知唔知咁樣會令我好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好想繼續鍾意妳<br />\n但我真係做唔到<br />\n點解我地要喺呢個時勢先相遇<br />\n點解呢個政府咁撚仆街<br />\n我真係好想同妳一齊做港豬<br />\n但我唔可以拋棄咁多位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點都好<br />\n我今日唔提妳啦<br />\n但咁多位<br />\n一間都要萬事小心<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"}]}